snippet.title: Stellar Transports
snippet.description: Master the art of space logistics and hone your crate handling skills to keep Stellar Transports from going bankrupt. Stellar Transports is a puzzle platformer where your job is to move cargo from the hangar to the incoming spacetrucks. Time is always running out and you have a quota to fill! Will you take care to stack the crates carefully or throw them in hoping some might end up where you want them? Find out, in Stellar Transports!
